                        fostering communities and creating unforgettable experiences.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        Founded in 2024, Event Sphere has grown from a simple idea into a comprehensive event management 
                        platform that serves thousands of users worldwide. We're passionate about bringing people together 
                        and making event discovery and participation as easy as possible.
                    </p>
                    <div class="d-flex gap-3">
                        <a href="/events" class="btn btn-primary">
                            <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt me-2"></i>Explore Events
                        </a>
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline-light">
                            <i class="fas fa-envelope me-2"></i>Contact Us
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1501281668745-f7f57925c3b4?ixlib=rb-4.1.0&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1170" 
